The paper presents a new design of an external memory for neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), neural networks (cs.NE), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of Lie group actions in the model also suggests a potential connection to control theory and systems (cs.SY), while the focus on memory and addressing could also relate to information theory (cs.IT).
